data.description: 2264 SQ FEET OF BRAND NEW SPACIOUS LIVING .... ONE OF THE BEST NEIGHBORHOODS IN HUDSON FALLS... WELCOME TO 4 LARK STREET.  4/5 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms! EVERYTHING IN THIS HOUSE IS BRAND NEW, WINDOWS, DOORS, VINYL SIDING, HVAC, PLUMBING, ELECTRICAL, FINISHED GARGE, FENCED IN YARD, ALL POOL EQUIPTMENT. There is an egress in the FINISHED BASEMENT. boasting 2 FAMILY ROOMS AND AN ADITIONAL LIVING ROOM in the basement. This house is gorgeous and a must see! This house wont last long in this market. Don't miss out. Agent is a member of the LLC. Superior Condition
